      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should reach out, but what's the point? everyone says it gets better but they don't get it. it doesn't feel like a phase, it feels like the world just stopped moving and i'm the only one left behind in the dark. it's just so exhausting to keep pretending that i'm actually living.",
